PrecisRe-appointment of IVY F. MATSEPE-CASABURRI, of Johannesburg, South Africa, and VULIMIRI RAMALINGASWAMI, of Delhi, India, as governors of the Board of Governors of the International Development Research Centre, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective November 22, 1998.
Attachments
precis:
Re-appointment of IVY F. MATSEPE-CASABURRI, of Johannesburg, South Africa,
and VULIMIRI RAMALINGASWAMI, of Delhi, India, as governors of the Board
of  Governors of the International Development Research Centre, to hold
office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective November 22,
1998.
